*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Define FENCE as a user function (no-op passthrough) for runtimes that support redefinition.
* SPITBOL has FENCE as a built-in and will error on DEFINE — include only for snobol4dotnet/one4all.
*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
               DEFINE('FENCE(FENCE)')                                               :(FENCEEnd)
FENCE                                                                               :(RETURN)
FENCEEnd
